snippet.title: Prime World PvE trailer
snippet.description:
Prime World is a competitive RPG that merges fast paced MOBA-style battles with long term persistent MMO hero development. You can equip and train your heroes between battles using collectible and upgradable talents, build a thriving economy in your city, and play together with your friends. You can even start your own clan!

Prime World steps beyond the classic three lane map of modern MOBAs -- there are currently eight game modes, with more to come: from fast and fierce PVP Outpost to cooperative PVE Challenges to dark and moody PVPVE Dragonwald.

To learn more about Prime World visit http://playpw.com
